  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Office Simulator</strong> is a comprehensive business simulation game that lets you experience every aspect of office life from daily tasks and employee management to office customization and company growth.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399040/extras/e19acbe135ff24f63a67de3e987fb6d9.avif?t=1766929107\" width=800 height=100 /></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start as an intern and handle real office tasks from meetings and emails to document delivery and coffee runs. Gain experience, get promoted, and climb the corporate ladder to build and grow your own company.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399040/extras/866c8a865dd25918e3dc06aaa855c80b.poster.avif?t=1766929107\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399040/extras/866c8a865dd25918e3dc06aaa855c80b.webm?t=1766929107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399040/extras/866c8a865dd25918e3dc06aaa855c80b.mp4?t=1766929107\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399040/extras/1a6181c4fc4e503baa3e5b9a1f35cf48.avif?t=1766929107\" width=800 height=100 /></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your office with new furniture and equipment to increase productivity and efficiency. Boost employee performance, expand your workspace with new rooms, paint walls, change floors, and fully customize your office. Build the perfect workplace and shape your company your way.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399040/extras/3c1cfd647d2a3147ac47cf2a3d435bd4.poster.avif?t=1766929107\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399040/extras/3c1cfd647d2a3147ac47cf2a3d435bd4.webm?t=1766929107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399040/extras/3c1cfd647d2a3147ac47cf2a3d435bd4.mp4?t=1766929107\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399040/extras/11c74f52fe4f72f5afb78023ad5159d8.avif?t=1766929107\" width=800 height=100 /></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Distribute tasks from awarded bids among your employees and delegate responsibilities to assistants. Develop and customize your workforce, analyze bids, and choose the most profitable projects to grow your company strategically.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399040/extras/621903e0091d374f78292acbc44d4701.poster.avif?t=1766929107\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399040/extras/621903e0091d374f78292acbc44d4701.webm?t=1766929107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399040/extras/621903e0091d374f78292acbc44d4701.mp4?t=1766929107\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399040/extras/c58812ef5a0d2c2f49f6e3d6f1b69138.avif?t=1766929107\" width=800 height=100 /></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep your character energized with coffee and timely breaks, restock office supplies, and repair electronic devices as they wear out. Ignore these needs, and productivity will suffer.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399040/extras/f8025475b9bad69b8c406a1da57aea71.poster.avif?t=1766929107\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399040/extras/f8025475b9bad69b8c406a1da57aea71.webm?t=1766929107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399040/extras/f8025475b9bad69b8c406a1da57aea71.mp4?t=1766929107\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399040/extras/e9a3cda636896b84ebc21364600d7f40.avif?t=1766929107\" width=800 height=100 /></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep your employees happy by bringing them coffee and helping them with their tasks when they need support. A motivated team works faster and performs better.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399040/extras/11f65899b5a9281a0fa3344d354b2006.poster.avif?t=1766929107\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399040/extras/11f65899b5a9281a0fa3344d354b2006.webm?t=1766929107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399040/extras/11f65899b5a9281a0fa3344d354b2006.mp4?t=1766929107\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Office Simulator</strong> is a comprehensive business simulation game that lets you experience every aspect of office life from daily tasks and employee management to office customization and company growth.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399040/extras/e19acbe135ff24f63a67de3e987fb6d9.avif?t=1766929107\" width=800 height=100 /></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start as an intern and handle real office tasks from meetings and emails to document delivery and coffee runs. Gain experience, get promoted, and climb the corporate ladder to build and grow your own company.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399040/extras/866c8a865dd25918e3dc06aaa855c80b.poster.avif?t=1766929107\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399040/extras/866c8a865dd25918e3dc06aaa855c80b.webm?t=1766929107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399040/extras/866c8a865dd25918e3dc06aaa855c80b.mp4?t=1766929107\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399040/extras/1a6181c4fc4e503baa3e5b9a1f35cf48.avif?t=1766929107\" width=800 height=100 /></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your office with new furniture and equipment to increase productivity and efficiency. Boost employee performance, expand your workspace with new rooms, paint walls, change floors, and fully customize your office. Build the perfect workplace and shape your company your way.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.